{"tid":772464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本Sony招聘遊戲測試員 時薪77蚊有雙休保險","createTime":"2018-08-08T18:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T22:28:59.000Z","uid":66943,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ccd20f6410d162de1ecca8a059127f29348524a","tid":772464,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T18:30:24.000Z","msg":"　近日日本Sony互動娛樂開啟最新招聘啟事，本次招募的是遊戲測試，時薪高達1100日元（約合港幣77元），享有各種Sony保險補貼待遇，周雙休再加節假日，而應聘者只需要玩遊戲，玩的好的還能獲得獎金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/022559_c4c308ae89f86c607e7dfb98e57ac59e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F022559_c4c308ae89f86c607e7dfb98e57ac59e.jpg&h=08613542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從頁面上的描述我們可以看到，這份工作的待遇可謂豐厚，除了令人心動的時薪，還有OT費、休息日出勤補貼、交通補貼、全社會保險，員工可以享受帶薪休假，也有額外的加薪，服裝髮型沒有任何限制，且共同享有公司活動。而應聘者的必要條件自然就是需要玩遊戲了，PS4、PSV、PS VR平台精通的遊戲越多越好，遊戲經驗豐富的玩家會有更強的競爭力，招募的截止日期是8月20日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sie.com/saiyo/part/part11.html?tkgpscom=dc_arbeit_ps_tw_20180807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sie.com%2Fsaiyo%2Fpart%2Fpart11.html%3Ftkgpscom%3Ddc_arbeit_ps_tw_20180807&d=f%2B%2FQirMgScEj7oV8hhiYmzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4edfe1f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sie.com/saiyo/part/part11.html?tkgpscom=dc_arbeit_ps_tw_20180807</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/0/07/Sony_guilty.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20081211110622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F0%2F07%2FSony_guilty.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20081211110622&h=7b77b7d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b75556b0cece580e7182a0f1fe7eb37a5f0c48d6","tid":772464,"uid":135336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T21:22:35.000Z","msg":"富奸應該會去見工"},{"pid":"33c72d3aead6951a7501ae160809d04170931cd2","tid":772464,"uid":146707,"like":0,